# Time Sync §5.1 - Single Anchor Convergence

direction: right

1 anchor: {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#E3F2FD"
  style.stroke: "#1565C0"
  style.font-size: 14
}

Offset error < 1 µs: {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#4CAF50"
  style.stroke: "#2E7D32"
  style.font-color: "#ffffff"
  style.font-size: 14
  style.bold: true
}

1 anchor -> Offset error < 1 µs: "direct subtraction" {
  style.stroke: "#4CAF50"
}
